not just the unknown but also

00:03:49.140 --> 00:03:52.800 align:middle line:10%
non-human intelligences.

00:03:52.800 --> 00:03:56.040 align:middle line:10%
>> This discovery in this
specific location is a huge

00:03:56.040 --> 00:04:01.710 align:middle line:10%
